      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"ArchivesinBlender-ExporttoRIBArchive\">Export to RIB Archive</h3><p>To export a geometry or a group of geometry to a RIB archive, select the objects, go to the object properties <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"28\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637727/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637751\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"object_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637727\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2a0b97ee-e779-4a2f-9858-106251d5ea11\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28 1x\"></span>, and under the RenderMan Geometry panel, select Export and then Export Object as Archive</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"414\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/export_rib_archive.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=126\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637727/export_rib_archive.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"127\" data-width=\"416\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637739\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"export_rib_archive.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637727\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"68471933-ba43-47cd-b71d-1e730ae24a71\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/export_rib_archive.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=416&amp;height=127 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/export_rib_archive.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=126 1x\"></span><p>You can also select whether or not you want the materials that are assigned to the geometry to be exported and whether or not you want to archive all of the frames.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637727/export_rib_archive_options.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637727/export_rib_archive_options.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"263\" data-width=\"404\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637742\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"export_rib_archive_options.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637727\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d8fd0f86-5528-4685-9a68-32a58378603e\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-warning conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"35cdb175-4ccb-42c3-adf6-42b3ac3aafdc\" data-macro-name=\"warning\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-error confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>If you anticipate needing to override the material that's on the objects in the archive, uncheck Export Material</p></div></div><p /><h3 id=\"ArchivesinBlender-ImportRIBArchive\">Import RIB Archive</h3><p>You can import a RIB archive from the Add menu.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"340\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/add_rib_archive.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=340&amp;height=149\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637727/add_rib_archive.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"149\" data-width=\"340\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637745\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"add_rib_archive.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637727\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8ee780a5-a963-4045-a058-eb890d5c7b15\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/add_rib_archive.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=340&amp;height=149 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/add_rib_archive.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695179&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=340&amp;height=149 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"ArchivesinBlender-OverrideMaterial\">Override Material</h3><p>If you want to attach a material to the RIB archive, you can do that using the Material Override panel in the object properties <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"28\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637727/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637751\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"object_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637727\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2a0b97ee-e779-4a2f-9858-106251d5ea11\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28 1x\"></span>. <strong>NOTE: </strong>if there is already a material attached on the object in the archive itself, then that will take precedence.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"414\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/rib_archive_material_override.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=91\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637727/rib_archive_material_override.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"92\" data-width=\"417\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637748\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rib_archive_material_override.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637727\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ab73598f-6ac0-4b3d-96a6-9eb8ec969f4c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/rib_archive_material_override.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=417&amp;height=92 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637727/rib_archive_material_override.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432695424&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=414&amp;height=91 1x\"></span><p />"
    }
